    CLI (ves -W) and the libVES_Event C API

[06/21/2026] jz@vesvault.com:
    libVES.c 1.35 / ves 1.09 - Post-quantum by default. liboqs is now required
    (configure fails without it; build --without-oqs to opt out), and newly
    generated vault keys default to ML-KEM-768 (FIPS 203) instead of ECDH.
    The default OQS parameter set moved from Kyber768 to ML-KEM-768 (Kyber768
    was removed in libOQS 0.12). Classical-only builds default to ECDH.
    Existing keys keep their own algorithm.
